1. Take an array and a number that needs to be checked if present in the array. If number is present,print number is found, else print number

code :


import java.util.*;

public class MyClass {
    public static void main(String args[]) {
        
        
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int arr[] = {1,2,3,4,5};
        for(int i=0;i<=arr.length-1;i++){
            if(arr[i] == n){
                System.out.print("found");
                break;
            }
            else{
                System.out.print("Not found");
                break;
            }
            
        }

    }
}
